K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-4: nus pa ltar mdo sde 'di'i don yang de dang
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-5: 'dra ste / sus kyang bgrang mi nus so //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-7: mdo sde 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi chos kyi rgyal mtshan du 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-8: brgya byin lha'i dbang phyug gi rgyal mtshan dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-10: mdo sde 'di ni yongs su mya ngan las 'das
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-11: pa chen po'i grong khyer du 'gro ba'i tshong dpon
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-12: lta bu ste / ji ltar ded dpon chen pos
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-13: tshong dpon mang po ded de rgya mtsho chen por
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-16: mdo sde 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi chos kyi snang ba'i 'od du 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-17: ji ltar 'jig rten na nyi ma dang zla bas mun pa sel bar byed pa dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-19: mdo sde 'di ni nad kyis gzir ba'i sems can gyi sman bzang por 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-20: ji ltar ri bsung can la sman gyi rgyal po
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-21: 'byung bas nad kyi sdug bsngal zhi bar byed pa
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-23: mdo sde 'di ni log sred can thams cad kyi 'khar bar 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-24: dper na mi nyam chung ba thams cad de'i rkyen gyis krags pa dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-26: mdo sde 'di ni sdig pa ma rungs pa thams cad kyi zam par 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401a-27: ji ltar 'jig rten na zam pas thams cad sgrol ba dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-1: mdo sde 'di ni srid pa nyi shu rtsa lngar
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-2: nyon mongs pas gdungs pa'i bsil grib tu 'gyur te
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-4: bla gab kyis shin tu tsha ba'i nyi ma sgrib pa dang 'dra'o rigs kyi bu /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-5: mdo sde 'di ni 'jigs pa med pa'i rgyal po chen po ste /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-6: nyon mongs pa'i bdud ma rungs pa thams cad 'joms par 'gyur ba ni /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-7: ji ltar seng ge'i rgyal pos ri dvags thams cad thul ba dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-9: mdo sde 'di ni rig pa'i sngags chen mo ste /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-10: nyon mongs pa'i gdon ma rungs pa thams cad 'jig
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-11: par 'gyur ba ni 'jig rten na sngags mkhan gyis
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-12: gdon med par byed pa dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-14: mdo sde 'di ni bla na med pa'i ba mo'am /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-16: 'khor ba'i 'bras bu thams cad bcom pa ni /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-17: ji ltar 'jig rten na ba mo'am /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-18: ser bas 'bras bu thams cad bcom pa dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-20: mdo sde 'di ni tshul khrims kyi mig nyams pa'i sman bzang po lta bur 'gyur te //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-21: 'jig rten na sman aanydz'a na zhes bya ba mig
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-22: na ba thams cad la phan par byed pa dang
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-24: mdo sde 'di ni dge ba'i chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:401b-25: ji ltar 'jig rten nas dngos po thams cad kyi gnas su 'gyur ba dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-0: mdo sde 'di ni tshul khrims nyams pa'i sems can gyi me long gsal bar @402a *//
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-2: ji ltar 'jig rten gyi me long gsal bas gzugs thams cad snang ba dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-4: mdo sde 'di ni khrel ba dang 'dzem pa med pa'i gos su 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-5: ji ltar 'jig rten na gos kyis lus sgrib cing g-yog pa dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-7: mdo sde 'di ni dge ba'i chos kyis dbul ba rnams kyi nor rin po cher 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-8: ji ltar lha bkra shis mas dbul pa thams cad la phan par 'gyur ba dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-10: mdo sde 'di ni chos kyis skom pa'i sems can thams cad kyi bdud rtsi'i chur 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-11: ji ltar yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa'i chus skom pa thams cad ngoms par byed pa dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-13: mdo sde 'di ni nyon mongs pa thams cad kyi chos kyi khrir 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-14: ji ltar 'jig rten na gang zag dag bde ba'i khri la phrad pa dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-16: mdo sde 'di ni sa dang po'i byang chub sems
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-17: dpa' nas sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i bar
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-18: gyi rgyan dang / bdug pa dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-23: bdug spos rnam par dag pa'i rigs phun sum tshogs
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-24: pa'i theg pas pha rol tu phyin pa drug la
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402a-26: rab tu bde ba myong bar byed pa ni /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-0: ji ltar sum cu rtsa gsum @402b gnam gyi shing pa ri tsi tra dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-2: mdo sde 'di ni ye shes kyi mtshon ngar can lta bu ste /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-3: nyon mongs pa'i shing thams cad gcod par 'gyur ro //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-4: 'di ni mtshon rnon po lta bu ste bag chags thams cad gcod par 'gyur ro //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-5: 'di ni shin tu dpa' zhing rtul phod pa lta bu ste /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-6: phas rgol ba'i bdud thams cad bcom pa'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-7: 'di ni ye shes kyi me lta bu ste /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-8: nyon mongs pa thams cad sreg pa'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-9: 'di ni rten cing 'brel te 'byung ba'i snying po lta bu ste /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-10: rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi 'byung gnas so //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-11: 'di ni thos pa'i gter lta bu ste /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-12: nyan thos kyi skye gnas yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-13: 'di ni lha thams cad kyi mig lta bu'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-14: 'di ni mi thams cad kyi yang dag pa'i lam yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-15: 'di ni byol song gi skye gnas thams cad kyi brten pa'i gnas yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-16: 'di ni yi dvags thams cad kyi rnam par grol ba'i gnas yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-17: 'di ni sems can dmyal ba'i bla na med pa'i mchog yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-18: 'di ni phyogs bcu'i sems can thams cad kyi bla na med pa'i snod yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-19: 'di ni phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi 'das pa dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-21: da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yab dang yum yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-23: de bas na mdo sde 'dis ni chos thams cad bsdus so //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:402b-24: ngas ni sngar gsungs pa ltar mdo sde 'dis chos thams cad bsdus par gsungs mod kyi /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-1: chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun la tshangs par spyod pa yin no zhes gsungs so ////
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-2: 'phags pa yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i mdo /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-5: byang chub kyi phyogs sum cu rtsa bdun ma gtogs par /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-6: gzhan gyis nyan thos kyi 'bras bu yang dag pa
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-7: nas bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-8: byang chub kyi 'bras bu'i bar du thob par mi
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-9: 'gyur bas sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-10: sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin gyi 'bras bu'ang mi mthong ngo //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-11: de'i rgyu de'i rkyen gyis tshangs par spyod pa ni byang chub kyi phyogs sum cu rtsa bdun no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-13: byang chub kyi phyogs sum cu rtsa bdun phyin ci
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-14: log gi rang bzhin ma yin pas phyin ci log
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-16: ngan par lta ba'i rang bzhin ma yin pas ngan par lta ba 'jig par byed do //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-17: 'jig pa'i rang bzhin ma yin pas 'jig pa yongs su 'jig par byed do //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-18: rang bzhin gyis yongs su dag par spyod pa yin
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-19: pas sems can dag mthar yongs su dag pa'i tshangs
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-20: par spyad pa spyod par byed do //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-21: byang chub sems dpa' 'od srung gis gsol pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403a-23: zag pa dang bcas pa'i chos ni zag pa med pa'i chos kyi rgyur yang 'gyur na /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-0: de bzhin @403b gshegs pas ci'i slad du zag pa dang bcas pa la /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-1: yongs su dag pa'i tshangs par spyod pa'o zhes ma gsungs /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-4: zag pa dang bcas pa thams cad ni phyin ci log pa yin te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-5: de bas na zag pa dang bcas pa la yongs
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-6: su dag pa'i tshangs par spyod pa zhes mi bya'o
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-7: // byang chub sems dpa' 'od srung gis gsol pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-9: 'jig rten mchog gi chos zhes bgyi ba /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-12: zag pa ma mchis pa lags /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-15: zag pa dang bcas pa yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-18: zag pa dang bcas pags mod kyi /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-19: rang bzhin gyis phyin ci log ma lags na /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-20: ci'i slad du yongs su dag pa'i tshangs par spyod pa zhes mi bgyi /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-21: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-23: 'jig rten mchog gi chos ni zag pa med pa'i rgyur 'gyur bas zag pa med pa dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-24: zag pa med pa la phyogs pas phyin ci log ces mi bya'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-26: yongs su dag pa'i tshangs par spyod pa'i sems bskyed pa rgyun ma chad pa nas /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-27: mthar 'jig rten mchog gi chos kyi bar du sems rtse gcig tu zad de /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:403b-28: de bas na yongs su dag pa'i tshangs par spyod pa zhes mi bya'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-3: sems can gyi rnam par shes pa lnga ni zag pa dang bcas pa'ang lags te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-4: phyin ci log pa ma lags la sems rtse gcig
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-5: pa'ang ma lags na ci'i slad du yongs su dag
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-6: pa'i tshangs par spyod pa zhes mi bgyi /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-9: sems can gyi rnam par shes pa lnga ni sems
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-10: rtse gcig pa ma yin yang gang zag pa dang
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-12: phyin ci log kyang yin te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-13: zag pa rnams bskyed pa'i phyir zag pa dang bcas pa zhes bya'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-14: ngo bo nyid kyis yang dag pa ma yin te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-15: 'du shes la chags pas phyin ci log pa zhes bya'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-16: de la ji ltar na ngo bo nyid kyis yang dag pa ma yin te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-17: 'du shes la chags pas phyin ci log ces bya zhe na /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-19: mo ma yin pa la pho dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-24: gos kyi bar du de bzhin du rgyas par rig par bya ste /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-25: de dag ni phyin ci log ces bya'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-27: byang chub kyi phyogs sum cu rtsa bdun ni rang bzhin gyis phyin ci log pa ma yin te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-28: de bas na yongs su dag pa'i tshangs par spyod pa zhes bya'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404a-30: byang chub sems dpa' gang byang chub kyi phyogs sum cu rtsa bdun las rtsa ba'ang shes /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-7: byang chub sems dpa' de ni yongs su dag pa'i tshangs par spyod pa zhes bya'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-8: byang chub sems dpa' 'od srung gis gsol pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-10: de la ji ltar na rtsa ba shes pa nas mthar phyin pa'i bar du shes pa zhes bgyi /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-15: byang chub sems dpa' zhu ba la dngos po rnam pa gnyis te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-17: bdag shes par bya ba dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-19: khyod kyis rtogs shing shes kyang sems can tshad med
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-20: pa snyed ma rtogs mi shes pa dag gi phyir
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-21: dngos po 'di dag zhu ba legs so //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-24: byang chub kyi phyogs sum cu rtsa bdun gyi rtsa ba ni mos pa yin te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-25: rgyu ni gsal bar reg pa zhes bya /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-26: bsdu ba ni tshor ba zhes bya /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-27: bskyed pa ni legs par yid la byed pa zhes bya /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-28: bdag po ni dran pa zhes bya /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-29: ded dpon ni ting nge 'dzin ces bya /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-30: rgyal ba ni shes rab ces bya /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-31: yang dag pa ni rnam par grol ba zhes bya /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-32: mthar phyin pa ni yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen po zhes bya /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:404b-34: shin tu mos pa ni thog ma sems bskyed pa nas /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-1: dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi bar gyi rtsa ba yin te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-2: de bas na mos pa ni rtsa ba zhes gsungs so //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-5: 'jig rten na sdug bsngal thams cad kyi rtsa ba ni sred pa yin no zhes bya ba dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-6: nad thams cad kyi rtsa ba ni kha zas ma zhu ba yin no zhes bya ba dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-7: zhal che thams cad kyi rtsa ba ni rtsod pa yin no zhes bya ba dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-8: mi dge ba thams cad kyi rtsa ba ni rdzun yin no zhes bya ba dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-9: byang chub sems dpa' 'od srung gis gsol pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-11: de bzhin gshegs pas sngar mdo sde 'di'i nang nas
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-12: dge ba thams cad kyi rtsa ba ni bag byas
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-13: pa lags so zhes gsungs la /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-14: da ni mos pa lags so zhes gsungs pa'i don ji lta bu lags /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-15: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-17: gal te skye ba'i rgyu la bya na ni shin tu mos pa yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-18: gal te gsal ba'i rgyu la bya na ni bag byed pa yin no //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-20: 'jig rten pa dag 'bras bu thams cad kyi rgyu ni sa bon yin no zhes bya ba dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-21: gzhan yang sa bon ni skye ba'i rgyu yin no zhes bya ba dang /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-22: sa ni gsal ba'i rgyu yin no zhes bya ba'i don yang de dang 'dra'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-23: byang chub sems dpa' 'od srung gis gsol pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405a-25: de bzhin gshegs pas mdo sde gzhan las byang chub
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-0: kyi phyogs sum cu @405b rtsa bdun gyi rtsa ba
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-1: ni sangs rgyas lags so zhes bgyi ba'i don ji
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-2: lta bu lags / bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-3: de bzhin gshegs pas sems can gang byang chub kyi
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-4: phyogs sum cu rtsa bdun thog ma shes pa la
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-5: ni sangs rgyas kyi rtsa ba yin no zhes gsungs
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-6: so // gang rang gis rig pa la ni shin
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-7: tu mos pa rtsa ba yin no zhes gsungs so
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-10: de la ji ltar na gsal bar rig pa la rgyu zhes bgyi ba lags /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-13: de bzhin gshegs pas bar bar ni gsal ba la shes rab ces kyang gsungs /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-14: bar bar ni dad pa zhes kyang gsungs so //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-16: dad pa'i rgyu dang rkyen gyis dge ba'i bshes gnyen la bsnyen par 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-17: de bas na reg pa zhes bya'o //
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-18: dge ba'i bshes la bsten pa'i rgyu dang rkyen gyis dam pa'i chos thos par 'gyur te /
K11D0119-2_H0368-2:405b-20: dam pa'i chos thos pa'i rkyen gyis lus dang /
